metadata.name: a calm before the storm
metadata.description:
It was an extremely foggy day. The entire continent was swallowed by thick and viscous air, as if foreshadowing imminent frosts. But there was also something magic about this fog. A beautiful calm before the storm. I had to capture it.

You will get the original picture with 4000x3000.

And the code. What code? Well, you might be the first to find out..
